title: Cranks and Goggles v0.12
description: Cranks & Goggles is a single player top down racing game set in late 1920' and early 1930's. Players can create their avatar and enter different races in England, Italy, France and more. By unlocking harder events, players will need to purchase and upgrade higher class cars to progress. We must say it looks much easier to drive these cars than it is. Each car has unique driving behaviour and handling difficulty, so it is a top down racing game with a simulation touch
